      <article class="entry">
        <h3>Welcome to Claviga.com</h3>
        <p>Claviga offers a wide range of sales, service and management
programmes aimed at realising the true potential of individuals,
teams and organisations around the world. In short, we help your
business excel!</p>

<p>Our training approach is to deliver sustained business results
for our clients, engaging their workforce and motivating the
transfer of learning to their workplace. We specialise in
increasing the Sales, Leadership and People Development skills
within your organisation.</p>

<p>Our consulting approach facilitates the process of designing and
delivering key organisation change within your business.&nbsp;</p>

<p>&nbsp;</p>
      </article>
